r-2\",\"children\":\"💭\"}],\"Pet replacement for former pet owners\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Former pet owners who cannot physically manage a live pet\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Former pet owners who cannot physically manage a live pet\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Emotional substitute after losing a pet\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Emotional substitute after losing a pet\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":[\"Claims about health and wellbeing are drawn from published research. See our summaries for\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"href\":\"/senior-research\",\"className\":\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"older adults\"}],\" \",\"and\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"href\":\"/kids-research\",\"className\":\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"children\"}],\". Interactive pets are not medical devices and are not a substitute for professional care.\"]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 max-w-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm sm:text-base\",\"children\":\"For an additional level of privacy, look for the following:\"}]\n21:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Indicator light when the camera is active.\"}],\" \",\"It should be impossible to record without a visible LED on.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Physical privacy shutter.\"}],\" \",\"A mechanical cover that slides over the camera lens is more trustworthy than a software “off” button. You can visually confirm the camera can’t see. This is uncommon in the pet-robot category; if not present, look for a clearly indicated camera-off mode.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Two-factor authentication on the companion app.\"}],\" \",\"A connected camera in your home protected only by a password is a weak link. If the app doesn’t visibly support 2FA, use a strong unique password and consider isolating the device on a guest Wi-Fi network.\"]}]]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Steps to take once you own the robot\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Connect it to a guest Wi-Fi network\"}],\", not your primary home network. Most modern routers offer guest networks; using one keeps the robot isolated from your phones, computers, and other devices.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"If available, enable two-factor authentication\"}],\" on the companion app immediately.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Disable cloud features you don’t use.\"}],\" \",\"If you don’t need remote access while away from home, turn it off.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Turn off the camera in the app when it’s not needed.\"}],\" \",\"Even when a robot uses its camera for navigation or legitimate monitoring, you usually don’t need it on around the clock. Many of these products (including the Enabot EBO line and Loona) let you disable the camera through the companion app and re-enable it when you actually want it active. Build the habit of toggling it off during private moments — meals, conversations, time in the bedroom — and back on when you need the feature.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Keep firmware updated.\"}],\" \",\"Most security incidents involve products running outdated software.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Physically cover the camera as a backup.\"}],\" \",\"If your app’s privacy toggle doesn’t fully reassure you, a piece of tape or a small sticker over the lens is a zero-trust backup. It costs nothing and you can verify it visually.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Review the privacy policy periodically.\"}],\" \",\"Manufacturers update their data practices, and the device you bought a year ago may not handle data the same way today.\"]}]]}]]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Where can I research privacy questions for a specific product?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"These are independent sources that evaluate connected devices for privacy and security:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"href\":\"https://foundation.mozilla.org/en/privacynotincluded/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Mozilla’s *Privacy Not Included*\"}],\" \",\"— reviews connected products against a published set of minimum security standards.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.consumerreports.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Consumer Reports\"}],\" \",\"— assesses data handling and privacy alongside other product attributes.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L25\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/privacy-security\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"U.S. Federal Trade Commission\"}],\" \",\"— guidance for consumers on connected-device privacy.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"pt-2\",\"children\":\"Also check the manufacturer’s own privacy policy on their product page. This is the authoritative source for what data the product collects, where it’s stored, how long it’s kept, and who it’s shared with. Read it alongside the independent sources above rather than instead of them — manufacturers are accurate about their own practices but tend to present them in the most favorable light.\"}]]}]]}]\n24:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Which products on this site have cameras?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":\"We mark products in our catalog that include a camera with a small camera icon on the product card. This is informational, not a warning — many buyers want the camera feature. But we want you to see it before you click through.\"}]]}]\n2b:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n2e:I[6869,[],\"IconMark\"]\n28:null\n2d:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Questions about Interactive Pets — FAQ and buyer's guide | Interactive Pet Marketplace\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Plain-English answers about interactive pets and AI companions: who they help, what they offer, how to choose, and how to think about camera privacy.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Interactive Pet Marketplace — Compare interactive pets and AI & robotic pets\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"3\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Honest comparisons of interactive pets, plushy companions, and AI & robotic pets for seniors, families, and gift buyers.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:url\",\"content\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:site_name\",\"content\":\"Interactive Pet Marketplace\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:image\",\"content\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/og-image.png\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"7\",{\"property\":\"og:image:width\",\"content\":\"1200\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"8\",{\"property\":\"og:image:height\",\"content\":\"630\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"9\",{\"property\":\"og:image:alt\",\"content\":\"Interactive Pet Marketplace — Compare interactive pets and AI & robotic pets\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"10\",{\"property\":\"og:type\",\"content\":\"website\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"11\",{\"name\":\"twitter:card\",\"content\":\"summary_large_image\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"12\",{\"name\":\"twitter:title\",\"content\":\"Interactive Pet Marketplace\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"13\",{\"name\":\"twitter:description\",\"content\":\"Honest comparisons of interactive pets, plushy companions, and AI & robotic pets for seniors, families, and gift buyers.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"14\",{\"name\":\"twitter:image\",\"content\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/og-image.png\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"15\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/favicon.ico\",\"sizes\":\"any\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"16\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/favicon-32x32.png\",\"sizes\":\"32x32\",\"type\":\"image/png\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"17\",{\"rel\":\"icon\",\"href\":\"/logo-mark.svg\",\"type\":\"image/svg+xml\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"18\",{\"rel\":\"apple-touch-icon\",\"href\":\"/apple-touch-icon.png\",\"sizes\":\"180x180\"}],[\"$\",\"$L2e\",\"19\",{}]]\n","/questions/__PAGE__":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[9504,[\"756\",\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\",\"104\",\"static/chunks/app/questions/page-1f374704d40e8be0.js\"],\"PageShell\"]\n20:I[8500,[\"756\",\"static/chunks/756-98a13f2d10827e2b.js\",\"104\",\"static/chunks/app/questions/page-1f374704d40e8be0.js\"],\"\"]\n21:I[484,[],\"OutletBoundary\"]\n22:\"$Sreact.suspense\"\n3:T1703,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Questions\",\"item\":\"https://interactivepetmarketplace.com/questions\"}]},{\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is the difference between interactive pets and AI & robotic pets?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Interactive pets usually focus on comfort, touch response, and simple engagement. AI & robotic pets generally add movement, sensors, or more advanced behavior.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are interactive pets good for seniors?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"A growing body of research suggests that interactive and robotic pets can meaningfully improve the lives of seniors — especially those facing loneliness, isolation, dementia, depression, or anxiety.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are Interactive Pets good for Children?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Engaging companions designed to entertain children and bring families together. Research has shown that Interactive Pets can improve the lives of children by improving Interactive Learning, Personalized Engagement, Empathy, Technology Skills, and many other areas.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do these products need Wi-Fi?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Some advanced models may use apps or connectivity, but many simpler interactive companion products do not.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are these a good gift?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Buyers often choose them for holidays, birthdays, or thoughtful gifts for parents and grandparents.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Should I be worried about cameras in pet robots?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Worried may be too strong, but cautious is reasonable. A camera-equipped robot that moves through your home is functionally different from a fixed security camera: it can travel into private spaces, it stays connected to the manufacturer's servers, and like any connected device it can be compromised by software vulnerabilities. There have been real, documented incidents — including one where security researchers demonstrated they could take over a major robot vacuum brand and access the camera without any indicator light, and another where a different manufacturer accidentally exposed thousands of users' camera feeds to strangers. None of this means camera-equipped pet robots are unsafe to own; it means the privacy and security features the manufacturer offers should be part of your buying decision, not an afterthought.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What should I look for before buying a connected pet robot?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Look for a clear, readable privacy policy that states what data is collected, where it's stored, how long it's kept, and whether it's shared with third parties. Look for products that process AI on-device rather than uploading everything to a manufacturer's cloud. Check the manufacturer's track record by searching for past security incidents. For additional privacy, look for products with a physical privacy shutter (a mechanical cover over the camera lens), an indicator light that activates whenever the camera is recording, and two-factor authentication support on the companion app. Physical shutters are uncommon in the pet-robot category; if a product doesn't have one, look for a clearly indicated camera-off mode. If 2FA isn't available, use a strong unique password and isolate the device on a guest Wi-Fi network.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What steps should I take once I own the robot?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Connect the robot to a guest Wi-Fi network rather than your primary home network. If available, enable two-factor authentication on the companion app. Disable cloud features you don't use, including remote access while away from home. Turn off the camera in the app when it's not needed — many products like the Enabot EBO line and Loona let you toggle the camera off through the companion app, and you should build the habit of disabling it during private moments such as meals, conversations, and time in the bedroom. Keep firmware updated, since most security incidents involve outdated software. As a backup, physically cover the camera with tape or a sticker when you want to be sure it can't see. Periodically review the manufacturer's privacy policy, since data practices change over time.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I research privacy questions for a specific product?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Three independent sources are useful: Mozilla's Privacy Not Included program reviews connected products against a published set of minimum security standards. Consumer Reports assesses data handling and privacy alongside other product attributes. The U.S. Federal Trade Commission publishes consumer guidance on connected-device privacy. Also check the manufacturer's own privacy policy on their product page — that's the authoritative source for what data the product collects, where it's stored, how long it's kept, and who it's shared with. Read it alongside the independent sources rather than instead of them, since manufacturers are accurate about their own practices but tend to present them in the most favorable light.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Which products on this site have cameras?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Products in our catalog that include a camera are marked with a small camera icon on the product card. The badge is informational, not a warning — many buyers want the camera feature for home monitoring or AI interaction. The badge is intended to make camera presence visible before clicking through to a product.\"}}]}]}0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$3\"}}],\"$L4\",\"$L5\",\"$L6\",\"$L7\",\"$L8\"]}],null,\"$L9\"]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":null,\"buildId\":\"acFLag9weJPW7aMMY7VNM\"}\n4:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"pt-10 pb-2 sm:pt-12 sm:pb-3 lg:pt-14 lg:pb-3\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell max-w-4xl\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-2xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-trust-700\",\"children\":\"Quick answer\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-slate-800 sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\",\"children\":\"Interactive pets are companion devices that respond to touch, sound, or movement without the demands of a live pet. They’re most often chosen for older adults facing loneliness, children not ready for a real pet, or adults who can’t have one. Research suggests they can reduce loneliness, agitation, and depression in older adults, and support empathy and engagement in children. Camera-equipped models add privacy considerations covered below.\"}]]}]}]}]\n5:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"section-pad pt-10 sm:pt-12\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-3xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"eyebrow\",\"children\":\"About interactive pets\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl\",\"children\":\"Who would enjoy them, what they o