e\":\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-2xl\",\"children\":\"What are the benefits?\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Gentle daily comfort\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Gentle daily comfort\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Realistic touch response\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Realistic touch response\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Safe for apartments and senior living communities\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Safe for apartments and senior living communities\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Allergy-friendly\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Allergy-friendly\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Easy for older adults to enjoy\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Easy for older adults to enjoy\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-2xl\",\"children\":\"All the reasons to explore interactive pets\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":\"Tap any reason to expand.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"details\",\"Emotional companionship\",{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[\"$La\",\"$Lb\"]}],\"$Lc\",\"$Ld\",\"$Le\",\"$Lf\",\"$L10\",\"$L11\",\"$L12\",\"$L13\",\"$L14\",\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\",\"$L18\",\"$L19\"]}],\"$L1a\"]}]]}]}]\n6:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"privacy\",\"className\":\"section-pad scroll-mt-32\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"container-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"eyebrow\",\"children\":\"Privacy & security\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"A buyer’s guide to camera-equipped pet robots.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\",\"children\":\"A camera-equipped robot that moves around your home is functionally different from a fixed security camera, and the privacy questions deserve more than a passing thought. This section is what we tell friends and family who ask: how to think about the trade-offs, what to look for, and what to do after the device is in the house.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8 space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Should I be worried about cameras in pet robots?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Worried may be too strong, but cautious is reasonable. A camera-equipped robot that moves through your home is functionally different from a fixed security camera: it can travel into private spaces, it stays connected to the manufacturer’s servers, and like any connected device it can be compromised by software vulnerabilities. There have been real, documented incidents — including one where security researchers demonstrated they could take over a major robot vacuum brand and access the camera without any indicator light, and another where a different manufacturer accidentally exposed thousands of users’ camera feeds to strangers.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"None of this means camera-equipped pet robots are unsafe to own; it means the privacy and security features the manufacturer offers should be part of your buying decision, not an afterthought.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"What should I look for before buying a connected pet robot?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"A clear, readable privacy policy.\"}],\" \",\"Look for explicit statements about what data is collected, where it’s stored, how long it’s kept, and whether it’s shared with third parties.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Local processing vs. cloud upload.\"}],\" \",\"Products that process AI on-device leak less data than products 