ormer pet owners who cannot physically manage a live pet\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Former pet owners who cannot physically manage a live pet\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Emotional substitute after losing a pet\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"mt-2 inline-block h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-trust-500\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Emotional substitute after losing a pet\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n1a:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600\",\"children\":[\"Claims about health and wellbeing are drawn from published research. See our summaries for\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"href\":\"/senior-research\",\"className\":\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"older adults\"}],\" \",\"and\",\" \",[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"href\":\"/kids-research\",\"className\":\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"children\"}],\". Interactive pets are not medical devices and are not a substitute for professional care.\"]}]\n1b:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 max-w-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm sm:text-base\",\"children\":\"For an additional level of privacy, look for the following:\"}]\n1c:[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Indicator light when the camera is active.\"}],\" \",\"It should be impossible to record without a visible LED on.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Physical privacy shutter.\"}],\" \",\"A mechanical cover that slides over the camera lens is more trustworthy than a software “off” button. You can visually confirm the camera can’t see. This is uncommon in the pet-robot category; if not present, look for a clearly indicated camera-off mode.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Two-factor authentication on the companion app.\"}],\" \",\"A connected camera in your home protected only by a password is a weak link. If the app doesn’t visibly support 2FA, use a strong unique password and consider isolating the device on a guest Wi-Fi network.\"]}]]}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Steps to take once you own the robot\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Connect it to a guest Wi-Fi network\"}],\", not your primary home network. Most modern routers offer guest networks; using one keeps the robot isolated from your phones, computers, and other devices.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"If available, enable two-factor authentication\"}],\" on the companion app immediately.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Disable cloud features you don’t use.\"}],\" \",\"If you don’t need remote access while away from home, turn it off.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Turn off the camera in the app when it’s not needed.\"}],\" \",\"Even when a robot uses its camera for navigation or legitimate monitoring, you usually don’t need it on around the clock. Many of these products (including the Enabot EBO line and Loona) let you disable the camera through the companion app and re-enable it when you actually want it active. Build the habit of toggling it off during private moments — meals, conversations, time in the bedroom — and back on when you need the feature.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Keep firmware updated.\"}],\" \",\"Most security incidents involve products running outdated software.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Physically cover the camera as a backup.\"}],\" \",\"If your app’s privacy toggle doesn’t fully reassure you, a piece of tape or a small sticker over the lens is a zero-trust backup. It costs nothing and you can verify it visually.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Review the privacy policy periodically.\"}],\" \",\"Manufacturers update their data practices, and the device you bought a year ago may not handle data the same way today.\"]}]]}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Where can I research privacy questions for a specific product?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"These are independent sources that evaluate connected devices for privacy and security:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"href\":\"https://foundation.mozilla.org/en/privacynotincluded/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Mozilla’s *Privacy Not Included*\"}],\" \",\"— reviews connected products against a published set of minimum security standards.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.consumerreports.org/\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"Consumer Reports\"}],\" \",\"— assesses data handling and privacy alongside other product attributes.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L20\",null,{\"href\":\"https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/privacy-security\",\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener noreferrer\",\"className\":\"font-semibold text-trust-700 underline hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"U.S. Federal Trade Commission\"}],\" \",\"— guidance for consumers on connected-device privacy.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"pt-2\",\"children\":\"Also check the manufacturer’s own privacy policy on their product page. This is the authoritative source for what data the product collects, where it’s stored, how long it’s kept, and who it’s shared with. Read it alongside the independent sources above rather than instead of them — manufacturers are accurate about their own practices but tend to present them in the most favorable light.\"}]]}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"details\",null,{\"className\":\"group card p-5 sm:p-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-semibold text-slate-900 sm:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Which products on this site have cameras?\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"aria-hidden\":true,\"className\":\"shrink-0 text-trust-700 text-lg transition-transform group-open:rotate-45\",\"children\":\"+\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base\",\"children\":\"We mark products in our catalog that include a camera with a small camera icon on the product card. This is informational, not a warning — many buyers want the camera feature. But we want you to see it before you click through.\"}]]}]\n23:null\n","/questions":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[7121,[],\"\"]\n3:I[4581,[],\"\"]\n4:[]\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}]}]]}],\"isPartial\":false,\"staleTime\":300,\"varyParams\":\"$W4\",\"buildId\":\"acFLag9weJPW7aMMY7VNM\"}\n","/_index":"1:\"$Sreact.fragment\"\n2:I[7121,[],\"\"]\n3:I[4581,[],\"\"]\n:HL[\"/_next/static/css/4dd59df00fa48bb6.css\",\"style\"]\n0:{\"rsc\":[\"$\",\"$1\",\"c\",{\"children\":[[[\"$\",\"link\",\"0\",{\"rel\":\"stylesheet\",\"href\":\"/_next/static/css/4dd59df00fa48bb6.css\",\"precedence\":\"next\"}]],[\"$\",\"html\",null,{\"lang\":\"en\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"body\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L2\",null,{\"parallelRouterKey\":\"children\",\"template\":[\"$\",\"$L3\",null,{}],\"notFound\":[[[\"$\",\"title\",null,{\"children\":\"404: This page could not be found.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"system-ui,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,\\\"Apple Color Emoji\\\",\\\"Segoe UI Emoji\\\"\",\"height\":\"100vh\",\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"display\":\"flex\",\"flexDirection\":\"column\